external_knowledge:
Key contributors: Authors who have written publications;
Realm of technology: Refers to 'Computer Science' in the context of research fields;
Specific position within our community: Indicated by a role ID of 0, which can denote a user role such as administrator or active member.

sql:
SELECT journal_name, impact_factor
FROM journals
WHERE impact_factor > (SELECT AVG(impact_factor) FROM journals);

SELECT publication_id, title, keywords
FROM publications
WHERE research_field = 'Computer Science';

SELECT publication_id, title
FROM publications
WHERE research_field = 'Computer Science' AND international_collaboration = 1;

